original: Listrup, Sven Wilhelm, prakt, läkare, Ronneby, f. 26/5/00 i Listerby, Blek. 1. G. 32 m. Frida Klara Alice Olofson. Barn: Sven-Olov f. 35, Johan-Olov 38, Karin Elisabeth Svensdotter 42. — Stud:ex. i Karlskrona 20, med. kand. i Lund 26 o. med. lic. där 34. E. läk. i Örkelljunga distr. tre mån. 31-32 o. 34, i Ödeshögs o. Åhus distr. 33, prakt. läk. i Matfors 35-37, i Ronneby sed. 37, tf. proviläk. i Tors-by två mån. 37, i Ronneby flera period, sed. 44, läk. v. sinnesslöanst. Tjället i Nävragöl sed. 42.
translated: Listrup, Sven Wilhelm, practitioner, physician, Ronneby, b. 26/5/00 in Listerby, Blekinge. 1st marriage in 1932 with Frida Klara Alice Olofson. Children: Sven-Olov b. 1935, Johan-Olov b. 1938, Karin Elisabeth Svensdotter b. 1942. - Passed student exams in Karlskrona in 1920, medical candidate in Lund in 1926, and medical licentiate there in 1934. Deputy doctor in the Örkelljunga district for three months in 1931-32 and 1934, in the Ödeshög and Åhus districts in 1933, practicing physician in Matfors from 1935-1937, in Ronneby since 1937, temporary provincial doctor in Torsby for two months in 1937, in Ronneby for several periods since 1944, physician at the Tjället mental institution in Nävragöl since 1942.
